SUMMARY:Easter Bunny Train - Strasburg Rail Road
DESCRIPTION:March 27 – 29 & April 3 – 5\, 2026 \nExcitement is in the air at America’s oldest continuously operating railroad. Easter weekend brings a sense of renewal\, from the smell of the fresh country air and spring flowers to the anticipation on the faces of little ones as they prepare for a journey they won’t soon forget. \nWelcome to the Strasburg Rail Road Easter Bunny Train\, a unique and memorable way to celebrate the holiday with family and friends. This train is extra special because the conductor is none other than Peter Cottontail. \nAs you travel\, the Easter Bunny will hop from car to car spreading Easter happiness to the little ones on board. And while seeing the Easter Bunny always brings a smile\, it’s the special Easter surprise that makes the little ones happy. Don’t forget to bring your camera to capture the moment or feel free to shoot a few selfies to share on Facebook and Instagram. If you tag @StrasburgRailRoad\, the railroad can share photos of your family enjoying your day on the rails. \n\n\n\nCANDY DROPS – Hosted by the Easter Bunny and his friends\, will occur at 12:00\, 1:00\, 2:00\, 3:00\, 4:00\, and 5:00 PM\, Friday\, Saturday\, and Sunday\, at a designated location along our pedestrian mall area. Children aboard the train will receive a colored wristband that will grant them access to a specifically-timed Candy Drop\, which will begin 15 minutes after the train returns to the station. (Note: There is no candy drop after the 6:00 PM train; guests with 6:00 PM tickets may attend the 5:00 PM time slot.) Immediately after your train ride\, head over to the candy drop area to try to collect as much Easter candy as possible! \nLIVE ENTERTAINMENT –This Easter\, get ready for laughs\, surprises\, and nonstop fun as Mister Boom Boom and Ridiculous Nicolas take the stage! 🎉 \nMake your way to the Town Square Stage and catch their wildly entertaining\, can’t-miss performances that will delight guests of all ages! \nCOMING SOON OPTION \nEASTER EGG HUNT SHUTTLE –Add on a shuttle ride ticket to The Barn at Paradise Station for their Egg Hunt! Times and capacities are limited and all ticket holders must have a shuttle ticket. Shuttles will bring guests back to the East Strasburg Station at the completion of the Egg Hunt. \nThese shuttles will be offered March 28 & April 4th only. \n*Please note\, if taking the shuttle\, you will be opting for that experience instead of the Candy Drop at the Strasburg Rail Road
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/easter-bunny-train-strasburg-rail-road-2/
LOCATION:Strasburg Rail Road\, 301 Gap Road\, Ronks\, PA\, 17572\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Easter Events,Holiday,Railroad,Strasburg Rail Road events,Strasburg, Pennsylvania
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Event-Egg-Hunt-Easter-Eggstravaganza.png
GEO:39.9830724;-76.1597641
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Strasburg Rail Road 301 Gap Road Ronks PA 17572 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=301 Gap Road:geo:-76.1597641,39.9830724
END:VEVENT
