SUMMARY:Lancaster City Scavenger Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Imagine turning the streets of Lancaster into a real-life adventure—solving puzzles\, uncovering secrets\, and winning prizes along the way!\nNow’s your chance! Introducing Lancaster’s Ultimate Scavenger Challenge\, created by Unique Lancaster Experiences—where discovery\, excitement\, and local charm come together. \n🧭 Your Adventure Awaits:\n🧩 Follow inventive clues through Lancaster’s picturesque and historic downtown\n🎁 Earn fun rewards as you complete challenges\n🌿 Discover tucked-away gardens\, arcades\, historic markets\, and more\n🛍 Access special discounts at participating local businesses\n⏱ Choose your pace—go head-to-head with friends or enjoy a leisurely journey \n🌟 What Makes It Unforgettable?\n👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Great for everyone—couples\, families\, birthday celebrations\, team events\, or spontaneous outings\n🎭 Hands-On & Entertaining—history comes to life through interactive games\, not lectures\n📸 Creative Challenges—snap silly photos\, solve riddles\, and compete for glory\n📞 On-Call Help—first-time visitor? A friendly local guide is available if you need hints\n🎁 Awesome Gift Idea—for Lancaster natives and curious newcomers alike \n📱 Getting Started Is Easy:\n1.Reserve your tickets—just one per player\n2.Check your email for download instructions\n3.Watch a quick briefing video to get ready\n4.Meet your team at the Welcome Center\n5.Dive into a one-of-a-kind city experience!\n🎟 Spots are limited—reserve yours today! Whether you’re exploring Lancaster for the first time or rediscovering its charm\, this scavenger adventure will change how you see the city! \n*** Please note that some days offer multiple start times
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/lancaster-city-scavenger-hunt/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Unique Lancaster\, 23 N Walnut Street\, Lancaster\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Lancaster City,PA,Tour
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/scavenger-hunt--e1751993312200.png
END:VEVENT
