SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Our Annual Easter Egg Hunt is coming up from 11:00 AM – 1:00 PM on Saturday\, March 28th at DOVE Westgate!\nThe morning kicks off at 11:00 AM with games\, food and a bounce house\, with the egg hunt immediately following at 12:00 PM (for kids 6th grade and under only). Please bring your own basket(s).\nThis event is rain or shine – in case of inclement weather\, eggs will be available for drive-through pick-up under the covered entrance in the front of the church.\n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
