SUMMARY:Lititz UMC Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Our Annual Easter Egg Hunt Extravaganza will be held on Saturday\, March 28 from 1-4 pm\, rain or shine. There will be free refreshments\, crafts\, prizes\, story time and pictures with the Easter Bunny. Easter Egg Hunts will begin for children ages birth to 2 years at 1:15pm; 3-5 years at 2:00pm; K-6th grades at 2:45pm. Raffle basket winners will be announced by age group before each Egg Hunt begins.\n\nWe can’t wait to see you and your family at this special event!\n\nFeel free to email questions to EducationDirector@LititzUMC.org\, or call the church office. 717-626-2710\n\n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
