DESCRIPTION:Join us for our 6th annual Community Egg Hunt at the Manheim Township Athletic Complex (2883 Weaver Road). The event will take place on the turf fields. We will have games\, crafts\, face painting\, DJ entertainment\, free popcorn\, and of course\, the egg hunt!\n\nDon’t miss the chance to meet Mr. Bunny and get your picture taken! This is a FREE event!!\n\nThe hunts will begin promptly at 1:115pm.\n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
