SUMMARY:Wild Women of Wine Ladies Night - Thorn Hill Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Happy April “Jewels” Day\, Wild Women of Wine!\nOn Wednesday\, April 1st you can pop in any time from 5:30 pm to 9:00 pm.\nFor the craft we are discovering Diamond Art! Make a sparkling bookmark\, choose one of our beautiful Mandala patterns and try this calming\, meditative craft!\nThis beautiful craft will require about an hour to complete–but so worth it!\nIf you don’t have the time or focus to complete a bookmark\, a simpler craft will be available in limited quantities!\nWe are definitely having Nil’s Funnel Cake Food Truck outside at this event. Enjoy Nachos on Cheese or Chili\, Chili Bowls\, Empanadas\, Funnel Cakes and Fried Oreos!\nFairy Hair Sparkle with Zarah!\nClick HERE to schedule your time with Zarah for your springtime sparkle!\nhttps://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0B4BACA623A6FEC70-62907323-fhsbyzarah#/\nA Spring Sipping Special for our Wild Women of Wine\, this night only! These wines are perfect for Easter!\n\n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar\n\nart
